ActiveAccount
=============

Provides active record like to ldap directories.


Example
=======

user = ActiveDirectory.find(login_id)
user.description = "I am a user."
user.save


Requirements
============

- Rails 3
- ruby-net-ldap


Requirements
============

Define ldap servers in config/ldap.yml (look at the example directory)


